    "Therefore, the design, development, and deployment of AI systems must consider the emerging features of human-AI co-learning and co-evolving through cross-task knowledge transfer, selforganization, and adaptive collaboration so that the ecosystem can coordinate its various components to adapt to dynamic and complex operating scenarios, ultimately improving the overall learning, evolution, and collaborative capabilities of the ecosystem [28], [102].",
